title: For Sale:  Yugoslavian M24/47 Mauser Rifle
postcontent: After WWII, the Yugoslavians took the M1924 Mauser rifles they had in service and reworked them to the 1947 spec which includes new barrels with Yugoslavian crest and modifiactions to the stock to remove the side sling attachment points.  They then put them away in storgae for the next war, which is where they were when they were imported to the US.  These are great shooters with perfect barrels.  This rifle is chambered in the powerful 8x57 Mauser cartridge.  Includes sling, ammo pouch, cleaning kit,unissued bayonet with scabbardand frog.  These are drying up and getting harder to find in this excellent condition.  5 round capacity.  Bolt serial number does notmatch the rest of rifle.

title: For Sale:  1943 M44 Trials Rifle
postcontent: For sale is a rifle I've had in my collection for several years now. It is a 1943 M44 Mosin carbine. This is one of approximately only 50,000 that were made for that year and were used on a trial basis before being officially adopted as the Model 1944 Carbine in 1944.This particular carbine is in very nice shape, matching numbers and has a pristine bore that is very bright with no pitting or counterbore. It also bears the features of the earlier M44s in that it has a single ear bayonet lug, and the narrow front sight base.I have never fired this rifle in the years I have owned it, so I can't brag about how accurate it is (or isn't). While the 1943 carbine isn't the rarest Mosin variant, they are indeed rare, and it isn't like you would just happen to find one anywhere like you could with other dates of manufacture when you used to see them on shelves everywhere.Price is set at $325. I can also have it shipped to you through an FFL. If shipping, prefer payment through Paypal so that way I can get it to the FFL and sent out even faster.No trades, unless you have any surplus M2 .30cal ball ammo, or a US M1-C paratrooper helmet (the helmet with fixed D bales for the chinstrap) with the 506th PIR spade stencils on the sides.
